 futuras caries en dientes definitivos<\/li>\n<\/ul>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;3.29.3&#8243; _i=&#8221;1&#8243; _address=&#8221;0.0.1&#8243;][et_pb_sidebar area=&#8221;sidebar-2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;3.29.3&#8243; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; _i=&#8221;0&#8243; _address=&#8221;0.0.1.0&#8243; text_font=&#8221;|300|||||||&#8221; text_text_color=&#8221;#000000&#8243; text_text_color__hover_enabled=&#8221;off|desktop&#8221; text_text_color_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; header_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; body_font=&#8221;|300|||||||&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;13px&#8221;][\/et_pb_sidebar][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section]\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Relacion entre las caries permanentes en dientes de leche y los definitivos La caries dental es un proceso infeccioso que aparece en personas de todas las edades y puede desarrollarse apenas erupcionan los primeros dientes temporales. Se caracteriza por la destrucci\u00f3n de los tejidos duros del diente , la que es provocada por los \u00e1cidos [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_et_pb_use_builder":"on","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","_joinchat":[],"footnotes":""},"categories":[29],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-51801","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-salud-bucal-en-clinica-del-sur"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/51801","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/clinicadelsur.cl\/wp-json\